 2020-00772020-02-29,  AAFC,  ,  ,  , 
ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectAgreement with British-Columbia in order to assist financially agricultural producers
PrecisOrder Authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to ENTER INTO AN AGREEMENT with British-Columbia and provide up to $600,000 in federal contributions to assist affected livestock producers with the extraordinary feed costs related to the excess moisture and flooding experienced during the summer of 2019.
